POLLEN MORPHOLOGY. — Pollen grains yellowish, as monads; prolate; exine ornamentation microrugulate and microperforate; equatorial axis (E) roughly 25 to 30 µm long; polar axis (P) roughly 14 to 18 µm wide (
Fig. 3
).

